Text: Hi PMP... can you seed the sas work book by ron cody ... It will be very kind of you if you can upload more material on SAS
Hi PMP, has the issue with the non-parametric tests been resolved with this new version?

Just tested it, got the same error: 

Error: no license to run Component Nonparametric Tests
Execution of this command stops.

Will try version 18, really need to run a nonparametric test...

Hey the way to perform Non-parametric tests without using the standard tool is:

Analyze --> Non-parametric tests --> Legacy Dialogs --> [your test]

It works the same, but it is graphically less nice.
